<p class="">I have studied the general difficulty. Therefore, I must come down to individual cases if the hon. Member will submit them to me.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6a90ebbc-3a3d-4195-9748-9ef36c69ba9e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
